# Global Project Rules

1. Before starting the backend server or running tests, always kill any processes on port 8080: `lsof -t -i:8080 | xargs kill -9 || true`.
2. AI recommendations (ItineraryService) must always be filtered against valid database IDs using the `filterRecommendations` method.
3. For missing resources, the backend should return 404 Not Found (via BusinessException with _NOT_FOUND code).
4. Maintain Luxury Glassmorphism UI throughout the application.
